    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Evocation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 120 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 round</p>\n\nYou hurl a bolt of light toward a creature within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, it takes 4d6 Radiant damage, and the next attack roll made against it before the end of your next turn has Advantage|XPHB.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 4d6|1-9|1d6 for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
